Dhaka needs to prepared , we ' ve been hearing that a major earthquake is due in our region . Sohel AhmedMonday , September 19 , 2011 11 : 19 AM GMT + 06 : 00 ( 22 hours ago ) There is nothing much any one can do if a quake with a magnitude of 7 to 7 . 5 and above rocks Bangladesh and Dhaka as the city ' s 80 % area is developed in an unplanned way .